Package ca.dominicmayhew.Pipe

Class Record

java.lang.Object
ca.dominicmayhew.Pipe.Record
public class Record extends Object
The object used by Workers to simulate use of a producer/consumer pipeline. Includes fields for ID stamps from the `Creator` and `Receiver`, and time stamps for when each `Worker` requested access to the `Pipe` and when that access was completed. Throws `ProcessingException`s if an attempt is made to modify a field more than once.
